# carvis Development Guidelines

Auto-generated from all feature plans. Last updated: 2026-03-08

## Constitution Constraints

- Preserve `ChannelAdapter` and `AgentBridge` boundaries
- Keep canonical run lifecycle state durable in Postgres and coordination in Redis
- Allow only one active run per workspace; queue additional runs explicitly
- Treat logging, admin visibility, retries, timeouts, and heartbeat handling as product behavior
- Require contract and integration coverage for adapter, bridge, queue, delivery, and lifecycle changes
- Default project specs and collaboration docs to Simplified Chinese; keep paths, commands, code IDs, and structured requirement IDs in their original form

